<p>
<note type="mod" resp="#resp1" n="0411003" target="#nkr_note_mod_0411003">一卷【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】</note>
<note resp="#resp1" type="mod" n="0411004" target="#nkr_note_mod_0411004">南吳月支國居士支謙譯【大】，吳月氏國優婆塞支謙譯【元】【明】，吳月氏優婆塞支謙譯【宋】</note>
<note type="mod" resp="#resp1" n="0411005" target="#nkr_note_mod_0411005">漢【大】，唐【宋】，此【明】</note>
<note n="0411006" type="mod" resp="#resp1" target="#nkr_note_mod_0411006">飯【大】，飲【宋】【元】【明】</note>
